### Constraint type mapping
Map Reify constraint expressions to libslvs geometric constraint types. This requires pattern-matching on the compiled expression to identify geometric constraint patterns:
- `distance(a, b) == 10mm` → SLVS_C_PT_PT_DISTANCE
- `angle(line1, line2) == 90deg` → SLVS_C_ANGLE + SLVS_C_PERPENDICULAR
- `parallel(line1, line2)` → SLVS_C_PARALLEL

