## What to build

Add Claude-specific state management and IPC wrappers to the GUI frontend.

1. **`stores/claudeStore.ts`** — SolidJS store:
   ```typescript
   interface ClaudeMessage {
     id: string;
     role: 'user' | 'assistant';
     content: string;           // accumulated text
     thinking?: string;         // accumulated thinking text
     toolCalls?: ToolCallInfo[]; // tool calls made in this message
     context?: MessageContext;   // attached context (user messages only)
     timestamp: number;
   }

   interface ToolCallInfo {
     toolName: string;
     toolInput: Record<string, unknown>;
     result?: Record<string, unknown>;
     status: 'pending' | 'complete' | 'error';
   }

   interface ClaudeStore {
     messages: ClaudeMessage[];
     sessionStatus: 'idle' | 'connecting' | 'thinking' | 'responding' | 'tool-calling' | 'error';
     currentMessageId: string | null;  // ID of the message currently streaming
     error: string | null;
   }
   ```

   Methods:
   - `sendMessage(text: string, context?: MessageContext)` — add user message, call Tauri command, start streaming
   - `abort()` — cancel current generation
   - `clearSession()` — clear messages, reset session
   - `subscribeToEvents()` — listen to all `claude-*` Tauri events, update store reactively

   Event handlers:
   - `claude-text-delta`: append to current assistant message content
   - `claude-thinking-delta`: append to current assistant message thinking
   - `claude-tool-call`: add ToolCallInfo to current message
   - `claude-tool-result`: update ToolCallInfo with result
   - `claude-done`: set sessionStatus to idle
   - `claude-error`: set error, update sessionStatus

2. **`bridge.ts` additions** — typed Tauri wrappers:
   ```typescript
   export function claudeSendMessage(text: string, context?: MessageContext): Promise<string>;
   export function claudeAbort(): Promise<void>;
   export function claudeClearSession(): Promise<void>;

   export function onClaudeTextDelta(cb: (payload: { id: string; content: string }) => void): Promise<UnlistenFn>;
   export function onClaudeThinkingDelta(cb: (payload: { id: string; content: string }) => void): Promise<UnlistenFn>;
   export function onClaudeToolCall(cb: (payload: { id: string; tool_name: string; tool_input: object }) => void): Promise<UnlistenFn>;
   export function onClaudeToolResult(cb: (payload: { id: string; tool_name: string; result: object }) => void): Promise<UnlistenFn>;
   export function onClaudeDone(cb: (payload: { id: string }) => void): Promise<UnlistenFn>;
   export function onClaudeError(cb: (payload: { id: string; message: string }) => void): Promise<UnlistenFn>;
   ```

3. **Types** — add to `types.ts`:
